    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the celebrated S54-powered chassis. The 3.2L atmospheric inline-six features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, providing an urgent, linear power delivery to the 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed\u2014critical preventative maintenance for this high-revving platform. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the tactile feedback and neutral handling balance the M-division is known for. This is a driver-focused machine with sorted internals and sharp throttle response.",
