      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances luxury with dependable performance. The exterior is finished in a deep metallic charcoal that retains a high-gloss shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a light scratch near the door handle, the body remains straight and free of any major dents. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free. The premium leather seats show light creasing on the driver's side bolster, but the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. All interior technology, from the dual-zone climate control to the touchscreen infotainment system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, backed by a complete service history showing oil changes every 5,000 miles and a recently replaced battery. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of reliable service. Includes two key fobs and all original owner's manuals.",
